    <h3>4.3 数据库索引设计</h3>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>表名</th>
            <th>索引名</th>
            <th>索引字段</th>
            <th>索引类型</th>
            <th>说明</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>users</td>
            <td>idx_username</td>
            <td>username</td>
            <td>UNIQUE</td>
            <td>用户名唯一索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>users</td>
            <td>idx_email</td>
            <td>email</td>
            <td>UNIQUE</td>
            <td>邮箱唯一索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>video_albums</td>
            <td>idx_teacher_id</td>
            <td>teacher_id</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>教师ID索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>videos</td>
            <td>idx_album_id</td>
            <td>album_id</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>合集ID索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>english</td>
            <td>idx_user_id</td>
            <td>user_id</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>用户ID索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>english</td>
            <td>idx_core_key</td>
            <td>core_key</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>关键词索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>review_state</td>
            <td>idx_user_eg</td>
            <td>user_id, eg_id</td>
            <td>UNIQUE</td>
            <td>用户和英语内容联合唯一索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>review_state</td>
            <td>idx_next_review</td>
            <td>next_review</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>下次复习日期索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>review_log</td>
            <td>idx_user_id</td>
            <td>user_id</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>用户ID索引</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>review_log</td>
            <td>idx_last_review</td>
            <td>last_review</td>
            <td>NORMAL</td>
            <td>复习时间索引</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <h2>5. 接口设计</h2>
    
    <h3>5.1 RESTful API设计原则</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>使用HTTP方法表示操作类型：GET（查询）、POST（创建）、PUT（更新）、DELETE（删除）</li>
        <li>使用URL表示资源，使用HTTP状态码表示结果</li>
        <li>返回JSON格式数据，包含状态码、消息和数据</li>
        <li>API版本控制：在URL中包含版本号，如/api/v1/users</li>
        <li>分页查询：使用page和size参数</li>
        <li>排序：使用sort参数，如sort=name,asc</li>
        <li>过滤：使用查询参数，如status=active</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>5.2 核心API示例</h3>
    
    <h4>5.2.1 用户管理API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 用户注册
POST /api/v1/auth/register
Request: { "username": "string", "password": "string", "email": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "username": "string", "token": "string" } }

// 用户登录
POST /api/v1/auth/login
Request: { "username": "string", "password": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "username": "string", "token": "string", "role": "string" } }

// 获取用户信息
GET /api/v1/users/{id}
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "username": "string", "email": "string", "role": "string", "avatar": "string" } }

// 更新用户信息
PUT /api/v1/users/{id}
Request: { "email": "string", "avatar": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "username": "string", "email": "string", "avatar": "string" } }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h4>5.2.2 课程管理API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 获取所有课程合集
GET /api/v1/albums
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "id": 1, "title": "string", "description": "string", "coverUrl": "string", "teacherId": 1 }] }

// 获取课程合集详情
GET /api/v1/albums/{id}
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "title": "string", "description": "string", "coverUrl": "string", "teacherId": 1, "videos": [] } }

// 创建课程合集（教师）
POST /api/v1/albums
Request: { "title": "string", "description": "string", "coverUrl": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "title": "string", "description": "string", "coverUrl": "string", "teacherId": 1 } }

// 获取教师的所有课程合集
GET /api/v1/teachers/{teacherId}/albums
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "id": 1, "title": "string", "description": "string", "coverUrl": "string", "teacherId": 1 }] }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h4>5.2.3 视频管理API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 获取合集下的所有视频
GET /api/v1/albums/{albumId}/videos
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "id": 1, "albumId": 1, "title": "string", "videoUrl": "string", "duration": 0, "sortOrder": 0 }] }

// 获取视频详情
GET /api/v1/videos/{id}
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "albumId": 1, "title": "string", "videoUrl": "string", "duration": 0, "sortOrder": 0 } }

// 上传视频（教师）
POST /api/v1/videos
Request: { "albumId": 1, "title": "string", "videoUrl": "string", "duration": 0, "sortOrder": 0 }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "albumId": 1, "title": "string", "videoUrl": "string", "duration": 0, "sortOrder": 0 } }

// 更新视频信息（教师）
PUT /api/v1/videos/{id}
Request: { "title": "string", "sortOrder": 0 }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "albumId": 1, "title": "string", "videoUrl": "string", "duration": 0, "sortOrder": 0 } }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h4>5.2.4 英语学习API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 获取用户的所有英语内容
GET /api/v1/english
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "egId": 1, "userId": 1, "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "isTaboo": 0, "textCnt": 0 }] }

// 获取英语内容详情
GET /api/v1/english/{id}
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "egId": 1, "userId": 1, "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "isTaboo": 0, "textCnt": 0 } }

// 添加英语内容
POST /api/v1/english
Request: { "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "comment": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "egId": 1, "userId": 1, "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "isTaboo": 0, "textCnt": 0 } }

// 更新英语内容
PUT /api/v1/english/{id}
Request: { "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "isTaboo": 1 }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "egId": 1, "userId": 1, "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string", "isTaboo": 1, "textCnt": 0 } }

// 根据ID批量获取英语内容
POST /api/v1/english/batch
Request: { "ids": [1, 2, 3] }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "egId": 1, "userId": 1, "content": "string", "coreKey": "string", "translation": "string" }] }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h4>5.2.5 复习系统API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 获取用户待复习内容
GET /api/v1/reviews
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "id": 1, "userId": 1, "egId": 1, "ef": 2.5, "interval": 1, "repetition": 0, "nextReview": "2023-05-01", "english": { "egId": 1, "content": "string", "translation": "string" } }] }

// 提交复习评分
POST /api/v1/reviews/log
Request: { "egId": 1, "score": 5 }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "logId": 1, "userId": 1, "egId": 1, "score": 5, "lastReview": "2023-05-01 12:00:00" } }

// 获取用户复习记录
GET /api/v1/reviews/logs
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "logId": 1, "userId": 1, "egId": 1, "score": 5, "lastReview": "2023-05-01 12:00:00", "word": "string", "meaning": "string" }] }

// 获取用户某日复习记录
GET /api/v1/reviews/logs/daily?date=2023-05-01
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "logId": 1, "userId": 1, "egId": 1, "score": 5, "lastReview": "2023-05-01 12:00:00", "word": "string", "meaning": "string" }] }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h4>5.2.6 AI阅读API</h4>
    <div class="code-block">
        <pre>
// 生成AI阅读内容
POST /api/v1/ai/reading
Request: { "prompt": "string", "title": "string" }
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "content": "string" } }

// 获取用户的AI阅读历史
GET /api/v1/ai/reading/history
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": [{ "id": 1, "title": "string", "prompt": "string", "createTime": "2023-05-01 12:00:00" }] }

// 获取AI阅读详情
GET /api/v1/ai/reading/{id}
Response: { "code": 200, "message": "success", "data": { "id": 1, "title": "string", "prompt": "string", "content": "string", "createTime": "2023-05-01 12:00:00" } }
        </pre>
    </div>
    
    <h2>6. 安全设计</h2>
    
    <h3>6.1 认证与授权</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>基于JWT的无状态认证</li>
        <li>基于角色的访问控制（RBAC）</li>
        <li>密码加密存储（BCrypt）</li>
        <li>Token过期机制</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>6.2 数据安全</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>HTTPS传输加密</li>
        <li>敏感数据加密存储</li>
        <li>SQL注入防护</li>
        <li>XSS防护</li>
        <li>CSRF防护</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>7. 部署架构</h2>
    
    <h3>7.1 开发环境</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>前端：本地开发服务器（Vite）</li>
        <li>后端：本地SpringBoot应用</li>
        <li>数据库：本地MySQL</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>7.2 生产环境</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>前端：Nginx静态资源服务器</li>
        <li>后端：Docker容器化部署</li>
        <li>数据库：MySQL主从复制</li>
        <li>缓存：Redis集群</li>
        <li>负载均衡：Nginx</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>8. 性能优化</h2>
    
    <h3>8.1 前端优化</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>路由懒加载</li>
        <li>组件按需加载</li>
        <li>静态资源CDN加速</li>
        <li>图片懒加载</li>
        <li>骨架屏提升体验</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>8.2 后端优化</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>数据库索引优化</li>
        <li>查询缓存（Redis）</li>
        <li>分页查询</li>
        <li>异步处理耗时操作</li>
        <li>连接池优化</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>9. 扩展性设计</h2>
    
    <h3>9.1 水平扩展</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>无状态服务设计</li>
        <li>分布式会话</li>
        <li>负载均衡</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>9.2 垂直扩展</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>微服务架构预留</li>
        <li>模块化设计</li>
        <li>接口版本控制</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>10. 总结</h2>
    <p>本文档详细描述了E-Learning系统的概要设计，包括软件架构设计、软件结构设计和数据库设计。系统采用前后端分离架构，前端基于Vue 3 + TypeScript + Element Plus，后端基于SpringBoot框架实现，数据库使用MySQL。系统设计遵循了模块化、可扩展、高性能的原则，为用户提供了良好的学习体验。</p>
</body>
</html>